
                                 Ferko
 

  What is it? 
  -----------
  
  Ferko is a Java based web-oriented course management system. Its capabilities
  range form coarse-grained tasks such managing course enrollments to fine-grained
  tasks such as creating assessment rooms-schedule, creating test sheets for 
  optical answer recognition, etc.
  

  The Latest Version
  ------------------

  Details of the latest official version can be found on the Ferko
  Project web site <http://morgoth.zemris.fer.hr/apiproz>.
  More information is available at development site:
  <http://morgoth.zemris.fer.hr/trac/jcms>.


